sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant DetectorIn as Detector Service<br/>(Input Analysis)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant GenSvc as Generation Service<br/>(TGIS/caikit-nlp)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant DetectorOut as Detector Service<br/>(Output Analysis)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS

    Note over Client,DetectorOut: Flow 1: Text Generation with Detection (Unary)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/generation-detection<br/>Passthrough headers
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC ChunkersService
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>DetectorIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Input content detection
    DetectorIn-->>Orch: Detection results (scores)
    Note over Orch: Check input detection scores<br/>Block if threshold exceeded
    Orch->>GenSvc: Generate RPC (TGIS)<br/>or NlpService RPC (caikit)
    GenSvc-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk output text<br/>gRPC ChunkersService
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked output segments
    Orch->>DetectorOut: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Output content detection
    DetectorOut-->>Orch: Detection results (scores)
    Note over Orch: Check output detection scores<br/>Filter if threshold exceeded
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(generated text + detection results)

    Note over Client,DetectorOut: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI-compatible API<br/>(vLLM/llm-d)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Passthrough headers
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /chat/completions<br/>Bearer API token
    OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>DetectorIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content detection
    DetectorIn-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response<br/>(completion + detection results)

    Note over Client,DetectorOut: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Passthrough headers
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC ChunkersService
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments
    Orch->>DetectorIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content detection
    DetectorIn-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(detection results only)
